-- @firstCounterRange@ will be written starting at an offset of 0 in the
-- bound transform feedback buffer. If the @addressRange.size@ of an
-- element of @pCounterInfos@ at index i is not 0, it will instead be
-- written starting at an offset equal to the 32-bit value found at
-- @pCounterInfos@[i].addressRange.address.
