-- Similar to
-- 'Vulkan.Core13.Promoted_From_VK_KHR_synchronization2.cmdWriteTimestamp2',
-- if an implementation is unable to write a marker at any specific
-- pipeline stage, it /may/ instead do so at any logically later stage.
