--     @commandBuffer@ is a protected command buffer and
--     <https://registry.khronos.org/vulkan/specs/latest/html/vkspec.html#limits-protectedNoFault protectedNoFault>
--     is not supported, @pInfo->dstFlags@ /must/ include
