-- | vkCmdDrawIndexedIndirect2KHR - Draw primitives with indirect parameters
-- through an address range and with indexed vertices
--
-- = Description
--
-- 'cmdDrawIndexedIndirect2KHR' behaves similarly to
-- 'Vulkan.Core10.CommandBufferBuilding.cmdDrawIndexed' except that the
-- parameters are read by the device from an address range during
-- execution. @pInfo->drawCount@ draws are executed by the command, with
-- parameters taken from @pInfo->addressRange@ starting at
-- @addressRange.address@ and increasing by @addressRange.stride@ bytes for
-- each successive draw. The parameters of each draw are encoded in an
-- array of 'Vulkan.Core10.OtherTypes.DrawIndexedIndirectCommand'
-- structures.
--
-- == Valid Usage
