-- | vkCmdDrawIndirectCount2KHR - Draw primitives with indirect parameters
-- and draw count through address ranges
--
-- = Description
--
-- 'cmdDrawIndirectCount2KHR' behaves similarly to 'cmdDrawIndirect2KHR'
-- except that the draw count is read by the device from an address range
-- during execution. The command will read an unsigned 32-bit integer from
-- @pInfo->countAddressRange@ and use this as the draw count.
