-- | vkCmdDrawMeshTasksIndirect2EXT - Issue a mesh tasks draw with indirect
-- parameters through an address range
--
-- = Description
--
-- 'cmdDrawMeshTasksIndirect2EXT' behaves similarly to
-- 'Vulkan.Extensions.VK_EXT_mesh_shader.cmdDrawMeshTasksEXT' except that
-- the parameters are read by the device from an address range during
-- execution. @pInfo->drawCount@ draws are executed by the command, with
-- parameters taken from @pInfo->addressRange@ starting at
-- @addressRange.address@ and increasing by @addressRange.stride@ bytes for
-- each successive draw. The parameters of each draw are encoded in an
-- array of
-- 'Vulkan.Extensions.VK_EXT_mesh_shader.DrawMeshTasksIndirectCommandEXT'
-- structures.
